'''Perivi John Katjavivi''', ni  umukinnyi wa firime [[Ubwongereza|w'Abongereza]] na [[namibiya]]<ref>https://africasacountry.com/author/perivi-john-katjavivi</ref> .   Yakinnye filime nyinshi   harimo ''Eembwiti,'' unseen na ''Film Festival Film.'' Usibye gutanga icyerekezo, ni numuproducer, umwanditsi, ukora kamera, umukinnyi, cinematografi akaba n'umwanditsi.<ref>https://maishafilmlab.org/maisha-mentor/perivi-katjavivi/</ref><ref>https://www.kweli.tv/authors/perivi-john-katjavivi?locale=en</ref> 

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Katjavivi yavukiye Oxford mu Bwongereza kandi afite barumuna be batanu. Se Peter Katjavivi ni umunyapolitiki n'umudipolomate wa [[Namibiya]]<ref>https://variety.com/2016/film/global/joburg-namibian-director-perivi-katjavivi-on-his-elegiac-drama-the-unseen-1201906893/</ref>, currently  umuvugizi w'Inteko ishinga amategeko ya Namibiya, nyina ni [[Umwongereza]] Jane Katjavivi.<ref>https://www.f6s.com/perivikatjavivi</ref><ref>https://www.okayafrica.com/namibian-film-the-unseen-perivi-john-katjavivi/</ref> 

== Umwuga ==
Muri 2016, Katjavivi yakoze filime ye yambere  ''The Unseen''<ref>https://www.africa-in-motion.org.uk/resources/we-are-tano-2/event/493/</ref> . Iyi filime yerekanwe mu birori byinshi bya firime harimo na Busan, mu marushanwa yabereye i Durban<ref>https://www.cambridgefilmfestival.org.uk/people/perivi-katjavivi</ref>. Filime yatsindiye igihembo cya Filime Nziza muri Innsbruck no muri [[Otirishiya]]<ref>https://allafrica.com/stories/201601130841.html</ref>.  Muri 2019, yakoze ''Filime ngufi ya Film Festival'', afatanya na Mpumelelo Mcata. Filime ifite Premiere yisi kuri 69 ya Berlinale muri Gashyantare 2019<ref>https://www.africavenir.org/fr/details-evenement/cal/event/detail/2016/02/27/african_premiere_the_unseen_by_perivi_katjavivi/view-list%7Cpage_id-765%7Coffset-15.html</ref>. Usibye sinema, yanditse kandi byinshi kuri ''Windhoek Indorerezi'', ''Afurika ni Igihugu'' na ''OkayAfrica'' .<ref>https://www.okayafrica.com/cinema-africa-perivi-katjavivi-the-unseen/</ref> 

